278
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,360
So a mistake is a mistake.

279
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,000
You should say to her

280
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:55,480
I'm sorry.

281
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,279
