285
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,879
I'll head back first.

286
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,399
Th-this, you're leaving already?
Miss Ruan?

287
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:18,759
Miss Ruan, goodbye!

288
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,679
Mom.

289
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,840
This way, this way, vertical looks good.

290
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,000
Yu, Yu.

291
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,279
Yu.
Last time you mentioned

292
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,919
the place for inspiration,
how was it?

293
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,279
It was great, the little courtyard was beautiful.

294
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,559
Let me show you.

295
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:21,360
Dad would definitely like it.

296
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,240
Look, there are even fish.

297
00:13:26,519 --> 00:13:28,080
This courtyard is quite cozy.

298
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,759
What do you think? Nice, right?

299
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:31,039
Dad would definitely like it.
You know,

300
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:32,879
this courtyard really isn't bad.
Suitable for retirement.

301
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:35,559
There's a little stove here.

302
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,159
I always sit around it.

303
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:39,960
See?

304
00:13:45,159 --> 00:13:46,000
Great writer!

305
00:13:46,519 --> 00:13:48,759
A day apart feels like three years!

306
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,080
Who is it?

307
00:13:50,279 --> 00:13:51,600
Why didn't you go to the village committee?

308
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,879
I even went to look for you.

309
00:13:54,159 --> 00:13:55,279
I just got back.

310
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,600
Were you looking for me to...
Well,

311
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:57,919
I have a question

312
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,639
I'd like to ask you.

313
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,720
Lately these days,

314
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:03,639
I've found while writing music,

315
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:05,399
I just can't get the rhymes right.

316
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,480
Here, let me sing it for you,

317
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,559
Just feel it for yourself.

318
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:14,840
Shishan?

319
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:15,879
What about my lyrics?

320
00:14:15,879 --> 00:14:17,399
I'm video calling my parents!

321
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,639
Maybe we can talk later?

322
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:22,000
Sorry, really sorry.

323
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,639
Auntie and Uncle,

324
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,799
Hello.
Auntie and Uncle,

325
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,720
Wishing you a happy New Year!

326
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,559
Happy New Year, happy New Year!

327
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,240
You go ahead then,
I won't disturb you.

328
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,679
See you later.

329
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,720
Yu,

330
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:40,000
that boy who came in just now,
who is he?

331
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:42,679
Is he a local?
What does he do?

332
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,440
Tell Mom.

333
00:14:44,879 --> 00:14:45,879
Stop asking.

334
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,480
What decent boy

335
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,960
would say "a day apart feels like three years"

336
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,559
to a girl he just met?

337
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:51,480
Just asking!

338
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:53,039
What's wrong with asking?

339
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,559
Alright, Mom, Dad.

340
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:56,559
He's

341
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:58,000
the brother of the guesthouse owner.

342
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:01,960
Although his personality is a bit unique,

343
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:03,000
he's a nice person.

344
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,279
Well, he's not as good as Xu.

345
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:05,759
Right.

346
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:06,960
Yu,

347
00:15:07,519 --> 00:15:09,039
are you still on bad terms with Xu?

348
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,879
We're not on bad terms.

349
00:15:14,639 --> 00:15:16,879
He and I were never really that close.

350
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,080
Well...

351
00:15:26,399 --> 00:15:27,200
Mr. Xu.

352
00:15:28,039 --> 00:15:29,279
I've been waiting for you for a long time.

353
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,039
I watched your legal aid session

354
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:32,159
at the village committee today.

355
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:33,559
I thought it was extremely professional.

356
00:15:34,519 --> 00:15:35,519
So I was thinking,

357
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,320
could you

358
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,799
help me with a lawsuit too?

359
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,080
You have a lawsuit too?

360
00:15:41,159 --> 00:15:41,799
Yes.

361
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:44,360
Alright, let's sit down and talk.

362
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,559
Okay, sure.

363
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:46,600
Help him take notes.

364
00:15:47,039 --> 00:15:47,519
Okay.

365
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:48,600
Actually,

366
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,240
it's not really a big case.

367
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:52,039
I want to sue my dad.

368
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,559
Sue your dad?
Li Shishan!

369
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,200
You're acting up again, huh?

370
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,440
You're hitting me again, right?

371
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,200
You're hitting me!

372
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,879
Hitting you? Hitting you is being lenient!

373
00:15:59,879 --> 00:16:00,759
Don't get physical!

374
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:01,879
What's wrong with having a dream?

375
00:16:02,399 --> 00:16:03,480
"Having a dream"?

376
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,759
That's just daydreaming!

377
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,440
Mr. Xu, I want to add a defendant!

378
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,480
I want to sue my sister!

379
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,960
Just wait till I catch you!

380
00:16:09,039 --> 00:16:09,679
I'll get you!

381
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:12,399
If I don't daydream, how can I have a dream?

382
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,840
What's wrong with having a dream?

383
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:15,679
You can keep my ID card,

384
00:16:15,679 --> 00:16:16,679
but you can't keep me!

385
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,080
Even if you could keep me,

386
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,480
you can't keep my heart!

387
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,279
Go and check it out.

388
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:25,480
Understand the situation.

389
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,039
Okay, okay.

390
00:16:34,039 --> 00:16:34,679
Go!

391
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:44,360
Mr. Xu,

392
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,720
About Li Shishan,

393
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,440
I've figured everything out.
Good, sit down.

394
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:48,559
Okay.

395
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:49,679
What did they say?

396
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:51,960
Well,

397
00:16:52,399 --> 00:16:54,159
he's a fan of Li Shican, right?

398
00:16:54,279 --> 00:16:56,279
So he also wants to sing and become a singer.

399
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:58,480
But his family doesn't agree.

400
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,240
It seems they're afraid he'll

401
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,039
mess around alone out there.

402
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:01,840
His father

403
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,120
even confiscated his ID card.

404
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,000
So then,

405
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:06,400
go to their house tomorrow.

406
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,480
Focus on mediation.

407
00:17:07,799 --> 00:17:08,400
No problem.

408
00:17:12,799 --> 00:17:13,839
You've been busy all day.

409
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:14,680
Hungry?

410
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,480
Yeah, a little.

411
00:17:17,039 --> 00:17:18,559
She must be hungry too, right?

412
00:17:18,799 --> 00:17:19,480
What did you say?

413
00:17:20,759 --> 00:17:21,279
Nothing.

414
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,400
By the way,
when you came back,

415
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,519
did you see Miss Ruan?

416
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:25,599
I did.

417
00:17:25,799 --> 00:17:27,759
She's in the kitchen with Cai,

418
00:17:27,759 --> 00:17:28,680
getting hotpot ready.

419
00:17:30,519 --> 00:17:31,720
Smells amazing, Mr. Xu.

420
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:32,480
But,
we should prepare

421
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,279
our own dinner first.

422
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,440
I'm so hungry right now.

423
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,440
They're preparing dinner in the kitchen,

424
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,599
making hotpot.

425
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:43,960
Didn't they invite us?

426
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,160
Cai did invite me when she saw me,

427
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:47,880
but I said

428
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:49,240
we had other plans.

429
00:17:50,319 --> 00:17:51,319
I figured it wouldn't be right

430
00:17:51,319 --> 00:17:52,480
to keep freeloading meals.

431
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,559
This doesn't align with
the legal aid principle of

432
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,559
"not taking a single thing from the masses."

433
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,480
You're right.

434
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,079
But what do you mean by "freeloading"?

435
00:18:02,559 --> 00:18:03,039
We should

436
00:18:03,039 --> 00:18:04,680
be a little more flexible.

437
00:18:05,359 --> 00:18:06,000
Think of it this way:

438
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:10,079
we could pay,

439
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,599
or we could

440
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:12,799
earn it through our own efforts,

441
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,200
helping them out,

442
00:18:14,759 --> 00:18:16,079
using our own labor

443
00:18:16,359 --> 00:18:17,359
to exchange for food.

444
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,440
Alright.

445
00:18:19,559 --> 00:18:20,839
Then let's go and work right away.

446
00:18:20,839 --> 00:18:21,799
But, Mr. Xu,

447
00:18:21,799 --> 00:18:23,079
if they've already finished cooking,

448
00:18:23,079 --> 00:18:24,319
what exactly can we do?

449
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,200
Do you eat cilantro?
I eat everything.

450
00:18:29,079 --> 00:18:29,799
Great!
I'll put in some extra for you.

451
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,359
You eat scallions too, right?
Yes.

452
00:18:32,759 --> 00:18:33,400
Good.

453
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,640
I like people who aren't picky eaters.

454
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,400
A little more scallion for you.

455
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,200
Cai!

456
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,640
Um, that, that Mr. Xu,

457
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:42,039
he, his stomach is upset.

458
00:18:42,039 --> 00:18:43,079
Do you have any stomach medicine?

459
00:18:44,319 --> 00:18:45,200
Stomach upset?
Why

460
00:18:46,039 --> 00:18:47,200
so suddenly?

461
00:18:47,839 --> 00:18:48,400
Yes, yes.

462
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,680
Under the bedside table,

463
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,480
there's a first aid kit,

464
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:51,759
with some regular medicine inside.

465
00:18:52,359 --> 00:18:53,400
Is it serious?

466
00:18:53,519 --> 00:18:56,240
He, he sh-should just be...

467
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,599
Is it cramping or...?

468
00:18:57,599 --> 00:18:58,279
It's not foot pain,

469
00:18:58,279 --> 00:18:59,640
it's stomach pain, Cai!

470
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,480
I know it's stomach!

471
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,799
I meant, is it cramping or burning,

472
00:19:02,839 --> 00:19:03,880
or, that...

473
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,599
Chen Hui, I've found it.

474
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,079
Under that bedside table,

475
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:08,000
I've already taken the medicine.
How is it?

476
00:19:09,359 --> 00:19:10,039
Not bad.

477
00:19:10,039 --> 00:19:12,119
It's probably just from irregular habits,

478
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,480
got too hungry.

479
00:19:15,519 --> 00:19:16,920
From hunger, huh?

480
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,359
Quick, quick, quick.

481
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,960
There's this big table full of food,

482
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:20,960
we can't finish it all.
Come on, join us.

483
00:19:21,599 --> 00:19:22,839
Alright, that's too kind.

484
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,279
Actually, no.

485
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,079
You have a stomach ache,

486
00:19:26,079 --> 00:19:27,160
you shouldn't eat hotpot.

487
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,839
Cai, don't worry.

488
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,640
For someone as capable as Mr. Xu,

489
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,880
hotpot is nothing—

490
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:34,079
he could even eat a pot of boiling oil.

491
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:36,279
Right.
Alright.

492
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,440
And I just made it spicy,

493
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:39,920
it warms the stomach. It's fine.

494
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:40,759
Eat, eat.

495
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:41,799
I'll go get you some bowls and plates.

496
00:19:41,799 --> 00:19:42,720
Thank you, Cai, thank you.
Sorry for the trouble, Cai.

497
00:19:45,119 --> 00:19:45,640
Miss Ruan,
I heard today's ingredients

498
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,240
were all bought by you.
Um, well,

499
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:50,480
we'll give you the meal money tomorrow.

500
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:52,079
Don't be so polite, it's fine.

501
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,279
No, we must.
This isn't polite,

502
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,359
can't we just

503
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:57,279
treat you back tomorrow instead?

504
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,640
Right, right. Miss Ruan, um,

505
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,839
we'll treat you tomorrow.

506
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:03,480
It's okay.

507
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,039
Look what this is.

508
00:20:05,799 --> 00:20:07,960
I learned to make apple cider from someone.

509
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,200
You guys try it for me.

510
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,119
Apple cider?

511
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:13,480
The alcohol content isn't high.

512
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:14,960
You can drink as much as you like.

513
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:16,759
You can't drink.

514
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:17,839
You just took medicine,
you can't drink alcohol.

515
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,799
A little bit shouldn't matter.

516
00:20:22,519 --> 00:20:23,359
Sis, it's fine.

517
00:20:23,599 --> 00:20:25,400
Mr. Xu knows his limits.

518
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:26,799
Alright.

519
00:20:27,119 --> 00:20:28,440
The alcohol content isn't high.

520
00:20:29,319 --> 00:20:30,079
Just a little, okay?

521
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,079
Got it.

522
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:32,680
Here.

523
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,160
Thanks.

524
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,839
How is it? Good?

525
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,480
It's very good, very fragrant, Sis.

526
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:38,759
Wonderful!

527
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,880
Drink up, there's plenty.

528
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,240
The fruit flavor is quite strong.

529
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:42,880
Right?

530
00:20:43,599 --> 00:20:45,000
No matter how much you drink this, you won't get drunk.

531
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,559
So you don't need to worry.

532
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,000
Perfect for cutting the grease from the hotpot.

533
00:20:52,279 --> 00:20:53,240
I'll do it myself, I'll do it myself.

534
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,359
Thanks.

535
00:20:58,359 --> 00:20:59,160
So fragrant.
Really?

536
00:21:01,079 --> 00:21:01,960
Quick, taste it.

537
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,359
That's enough.
Too much.

538
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,160
See?
What's wrong?

539
00:21:11,359 --> 00:21:12,920
The wind's making me a bit dizzy.

540
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:14,319
Mr. Chen,

541
00:21:14,319 --> 00:21:16,200
I think your tolerance is still not great.

542
00:21:16,279 --> 00:21:18,319
I don't feel anything after drinking it.

543
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,319
You said...
Come on, Miss Ruan.

544
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,000
Now this isn't right.

545
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,119
I have to be polite,

546
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:24,640
you know?
Come on.

547
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:26,200
No, no, no.

548
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,559
Chen.

549
00:21:27,559 --> 00:21:28,799
Come on, let me help you up.

550
00:21:28,799 --> 00:21:29,480
I'll take you back first.

551
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:30,799
Come on, come on, let me help you up.

552
00:21:30,799 --> 00:21:31,759
Okay, I am a bit dizzy.

553
00:21:31,759 --> 00:21:33,079
I, I'll go back first.

554
00:21:33,079 --> 00:21:33,680
Miss Ruan,

555
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,440
you don't need to help me.

556
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,160
I can go back by myself.
No helping, no helping.

557
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:37,880
Mr. Xu, you enjoy your meal.

558
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,680
I'll go back now.

559
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,759
Cai, I'm going back.

560
00:21:39,759 --> 00:21:40,559
I don't need...

561
00:21:40,559 --> 00:21:41,759
I don't need anyone to help me.

562
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:42,960
Watch your step.

563
00:21:43,559 --> 00:21:44,519
Take your time eating, Mr. Xu.

564
00:21:44,519 --> 00:21:45,559
Go on, go.

565
00:21:51,039 --> 00:21:52,160
Then I'll walk you back too.

566
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:58,599
Ruan Yu.

567
